All DFT calculations were carried out with the Gaussian 16 software. The optimized geometric configurations for each molecule were determined by the 6–31 + G (d, p) basis set. The B3LYP functional was adopted in calculations. The binding energy (E) was calculated by Eq. (4):4\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
